Summary: 3 Orange Orbs in a row and they disappeared one by one in a row about 1 second apart
trends: There has been one other sighting in Delran

divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving on Rt 130 and Bridgeboro Rd on a clear night around 6:00pm and I saw in front of me to the left through my windshield up in the sky at an unknown distance, 3 orange spheres of light in a horizontal row, just floating there for about 10 seconds and then they dissapeard 1 by 1 in a row and I did not see them after that. I tried to turn down a road to see if I could see what it was and I did not find anything in the sky at all.
